= Contact =

Please consider first to send your questions/remarks/bug reports, etc. to our [https://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/micro-manager-general  mailing list]. Having these communications in a publicly searchable mailing list rather than in private email will allow others to find the answers to their questions. If you consider you comunication private, please direct it to [mailto:info@micro-manager.org info@micro-manager.org]. 

'''Important:''' Please do not contact us using our personal email addresses with Micro-Manager support questions. Likewise, please do not call us by phone concerning Micro-Manager support. Commerical support for Micro-Manager is available from the company [http://missionbayimaging.com/ Mission Bay Software]. Services provided include subscription-based configuration support as well as custom software development.
